text.section:
This section applies to the transfer of the title or interest of an owner in a vehicle if the vehicle is registered in the:
Joint names of a husband and wife and is transferred to the individual name of either spouse;
Individual name of either spouse and is transferred to their joint names or to the individual name of the other spouse;
Joint names of a parent and child and is transferred to the individual name of either party;
Name of an individual and is transferred to the joint names of that individual and the individual's parent or child; or
Name of an individual and is transferred to the name of a child or parent of that individual.
